var UcNrn=class{constructor(a,b,c){this.qdb=a;this.ZT="\n                Survey to help refactor the document. This is just a starting point — do NOT proceed with edits yet.\n                For EACH option the user selected above, issue a follow-up survey via the 'ask_clarifying_questions' tool to gather the specifics needed before any edits. Bundle the questions for one selection into a single \"ask_clarifying_questions\" call (one survey per topic), and run those surveys sequentially — wait for the user to submit one before issuing the next.\n                Prefer SingleSelect / MultiSelect questions with concrete options derived from the current canvas (e.g. the actual colors, fonts, or labels in use) over open-ended text questions. Only ask for free-form input when the answer truly cannot be enumerated.\n                After all follow-up surveys are answered, summarize the planned changes and confirm before executing.\n            ";
